item.description:
If change streaming is enabled on a table, changes to the table can be processed using a Watcher Lambda function. Only tables can be watched, not secondary indexes.
To create a watcher, call the Watcher() method on a service builder.
// Create a watcher watcher := service.Watcher(&quot;process-changes&quot;, func(ctx context.Context, evt events.DynamoDBEvent) error { // ... }) // Watch for changes on the table watcher.Watch(table, strm.StartingPositionTrimHorizon)
